{"tid":335730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[06:34] 哥迪奧拿：NBA有控球後衛，曼城為什麼不可以有？","createTime":"2017-07-25T21:17:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T16:30:35.000Z","uid":28938,"like":48,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d49cad7d5125d4ec41530de129b7c243dd5275b","tid":335730,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T21:17:56.000Z","msg":"<strong>[06:34] 哥迪奧拿：NBA有控球後衛，曼城為什麼不可以有？<br />\n</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/051417_75ac6141fdc21aa2147f0462b5dc9100.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F051417_75ac6141fdc21aa2147f0462b5dc9100.jpg&h=0d9f84bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n即使首年登陸英超戰績未如人意，曼城主帥哥迪奧拿仍獲得管理層支持，於今夏獲大開水喉招兵買馬。繼早前以4,500萬鎊由熱刺收購右閘基爾獲加後，再分別以5,200萬鎊和2,650萬鎊從摩納哥與皇馬引進左閘文迪和右閘丹尼路，加上去季高價收購的史東斯，曼城這條億萬後防線實在令人期待。<br />\n<br />\n哥帥最近在接受法國Nineup報訪問中，提到這條後防線將大打控球戰術，將為英超球迷帶來耳目一新的感覺。<br />\n<br />\n哥迪奧拿興奮地說道：「我去年偶然地看了一場NBA直播球賽，看見史提芬居里如何控制全場節奏並成為得分王，那一刻我內心就明白了，己方後防往往是受到敵方最少壓力的，後防球員最有可能從容地控球；因此進攻的起點是後防。NBA有控球後衛，曼城為什麼不可以有？」<br />\n<br />\n「新一季曼城的進攻將由守門員開始，他會慢慢控球，並和後防球員撞牆，慢慢地引球到對方前線，然後射門、入球，就是這麼簡單。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/26/051617_67d57a07ceb7a0ddec212df7acb7d994.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F26%2F051617_67d57a07ceb7a0ddec212df7acb7d994.jpg&h=0b5369c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記者感到不解，問道：「防守和進攻由守門員和後衛包辦，那麼中場和前鋒又可擔當什麼角色呢？」哥帥以一個饒有玩味的答案回應：「他們在場邊為那隻退化的猩猩唱生日歌。」"},{"pid":"cf58cd8967239511d32c2da1406542e278198043","tid":335730,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T21:20:16.000Z","msg":"戰術大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c536c3cd67ab43807b8a799bd6f152481e3c154c","tid":335730,"uid":130531,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T21:26:28.000Z","msg":"佢傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"25ac3caa16199b840ed44bf238c1d6044b5a248e","tid":335730,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:20:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>戰術大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n等睇石頭入波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a7f52b73475958495579a3d45e6f906656e069a","tid":335730,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:20:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢傻撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢講得好有point，唔知你嘈咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85f8809558b1aa0f2898e641cab7b5b1e256c0bd","tid":335730,"uid":61660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:24:44.000Z","msg":"二公子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"381b3ac60d1bd5cd86abc3d56a49e390e738a4f9","tid":335730,"uid":37197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:26:11.000Z","msg":"唔明最後果句想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b1c1ef0cef6f52fed64878819bc30ee839c226c","tid":335730,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:28:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>二公子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n曼城= 魏國<br />\n<br />\n哥帥=楊修"},{"pid":"35b5f2f7141fdcfb207f20c57125b836f31cbeb0","tid":335730,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:29:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明最後果句想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2014年5月20日 下午04:28:00<br />\n<br />\n耶耶托尼經理人認為其客戶得不到應有的尊重......<br />\n<br />\n曼城中場耶耶托尼今季表現出色，帶領球隊分別贏得聯賽盃以及英超聯賽冠軍。但近日有傳這位球隊重心將於今夏會離隊，並打算減薪返回巴塞隆拿。來自英國《太陽報》消息，這次鬧出離隊風波的導火線竟然是耶耶托尼的31歲生日！<br />\n<br />\n原來這位中場的生日正正適逢球隊慶祝奪得英超冠軍的慶典，球會似乎太過沈醉於喜悅中，卻忘記了他的生日。耶耶托尼經理人接受國《太陽報》報訪問時，認為其客戶在球隊得不到應有的尊重，這次事件只是其中一個例子。<br />\n<br />\n「耶耶托尼感到傷心，有時候人與人之間的關係是金錢買不到，這次的事件反映我的客戶在球隊得不到應有的尊重，他很大可能會在夏季離隊。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=oViV65MKjtusFbMuXh0bSdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d18ccadc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"74d4ae00e130a8bb2e40c7ed9617afed177c2b17","tid":335730,"uid":89523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:31:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9ddfa0b694b5e97a3709af9b3bb4b2860e0e18c","tid":335730,"uid":12034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:31:51.000Z","msg":"下次加油"},{"pid":"acee23306286460a7b2d43fb9be00f3feff4543a","tid":335730,"uid":73340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:32:21.000Z","msg":"理念幾好<br />\n但石頭做到成個炸彈咁"},{"pid":"129d5f6f67509998a8811826e3f44a4b1d0275c2","tid":335730,"uid":5549,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:34:01.000Z","msg":"最尾果句over左，冇既就作得幾好，60分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29dc4464918bbaa71b47d5e008132f4338429d42","tid":335730,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:34:16.000Z","msg":"最後一句笑撚死"},{"pid":"81dc6a116ca3edbed0cbcd6f7ac8b771925d8393","tid":335730,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T22:34:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>理念幾好<br />\n但石頭做到成個炸彈咁</blockquote><br />\